column1: IF ccr_s_at_d is MF 0 AND ccr_testosterone_d is MF 1 AND ccr_etio_d is MF 0 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1
IF ccr_l6a_oh_dha_d is MF 2 AND cr_l8_oh_f_d is MF 2 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0
IF ccr_sa_dihydrotest_d is MF 0 AND ccr_a_cortolone_d is MF 0 AND ccr_b_cortolone_d is MF 1 THEN 2_Normal is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 4_Obese is MF 1
IF ccr_thf_d is MF 0 AND ccr_dha_d is MF 1 THEN 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1 AND 2_Normal is MF 0
IF ccr_pt_d is MF 0 AND ccr_llb_oh_andro_d is MF 0 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0 AND 3_Surpoid is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 1
ELSE : 1_SousPoid is 0  2_Normal is 1  3_Surpoid is 1  4_Obese is 0  5_ExtremeObese is 1
